Old Point Trust & Financial Services, NA

                    Old Point Trust & Financial Services gives consideration to the diversification among bonds and stocks as well as industry groupings within equity portions. With regard to fixed-income assets, quality standards and maturity patterns are developed. For municipal and corporate bonds, each must be rated 'A' or better. The maturity pattern is staggered so that the bonds do not all mature during the same period.                  




