Robert F. Shuford Jr.EVP and Director , Old Point Financial CorporationAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships52$334,400As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Robert F. Shuford, Jr., also known as Rob, has been Chief Executive Officer and President at Old Point National Bank of Phoebus, a subsidiary of Old Point Financial Corporation since September 8, 2015. He has been Executive Vice President at Old Point Financial Corporation since 2015. He has been Executive Vice President of Old Point National Bank of Phoebus since 2015. Mr. Shuford served as the Chief Operating Officer and Executive Vice President at The Old Point ... National Bank of Phoebus since 2003 and July 2012 respectively. Mr. Shuford served as Chief Operating Officer at Old Point Financial Corporation and served as its Senior Vice President of Operations. He served as Vice-President of Old Point National Bank. He has been a Director of The Old Point National Bank of Phoebus and Old Point Financial Corporation since January 13, 2009. He serves as Board Member of Arc Of The Virginia Peninsula Inc. He serves on the boards of the Peninsula YMCA, Hampton History Museum Association and the Virginia Bankers Association School of Bank Management. He is a Member of the Virginia Peninsula Rotary Club, Hampton 2010 Commemorative Committee and Hampton Forward. He earned BS in biomedical engineering from Duke University. Mr. Shuford is also a graduate of the Virginia Bankers Association of Bank Management as well as the BAI Graduate School of Bank Operations and Technology.Read Full Background




