Robert F. Shuford Jr.
Executive Compensation
As President and CEO (Bank), Director at OLD POINT FINANCIAL CORP, Robert F. Shuford Jr. made $330,600 in total compensation.  Of this total $300,000 was received as a salary, $20,000 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $0 was awarded as stock and $10,600 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


