Robert F. Shuford, Jr.

Age : 51Public asset : 788,923 USDLinked companies :  Old Point Financial Corporation 





Summary 



Mr. Robert F. Shuford, Jr., is President & Chief Executive Officer at Old Point National Bank of Phoebus.He is on the Board of Directors at Old Point Financial Corp. and Peninsula Metropolitan YMCA.He received his undergraduate degree from Duke University and an undergraduate degree from Virginia Bankers Association School of Bank Management.



Current positions of Robert F. Shuford, Jr. 









 NameTitle
Since
Old Point National Bank of Phoebus
President & Chief Executive Officer
2009 Old Point Financial Corporation(Banks)
Director
2003Peninsula Metropolitan YMCA
Director
